title: dominKNITtrix: Whip your Knitting into Shape
description: Features solid knitting advice with a hip, irreverent attitude * Perfect for beginners and intermediate knitters * On trend--speaks to a "new school" of knitters who want to infuse renegade spirit in their crafting projects *Fun package--bound in "leather" this sexy and campy design is sure to be talked about by hip, cutting-edge crafters Not your mother's knitting book, DomiKNITrix is all about bringing discipline to knitting and then using that discipline to create funky and hip projects that knitters want to wear, use, and give away with pride. Based on the popular Web site of the same name, this book will show hip crafters fun ways to tweak designs and give them a unique edge. More than just a collection of projects, this book gives you all the information you need to become an accomplished knitter in terms of tips, techniques, things to avoid--all in a fun and useful package."
